{"tid":1480034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得聽日內地黑衣人既目標係警察？","createTime":"2019-08-17T06:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:29:19.000Z","uid":78635,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d903fe061291160d9e30fa1ae15c6f03f7625d1f","tid":1480034,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"現階段再攻擊示威者已經無作用<br />\n國際民意已經係哂我地依邊<br />\n再攻擊示威者只會令國際更加企示威者果邊<br />\n唯一內地黑衣人落黎既目的<br />\n就係扮成示威者攻擊警察<br />\n可以預示到到時會有警察重傷甚至成亡<br />\n到時歐美國家就會處位一個尷尬位置<br />\n有可能影響到民主及人權法案通過<br />\n令香港萬劫不復 香港人世世代代被共產黨統治"},{"pid":"5e437ccf854c4d69891156fb60f8fe3f2c47f32b","tid":1480034,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"652c9f9a551070343debf527e1e6dcccf670f3b9","tid":1480034,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日 維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔衝唔搞事 和理非主場<br />\n懷疑係鬼 唔好同佢嘈 請佢立即離開</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5O6XQFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5O6XQFY.jpg&h=68680a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQwwU7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQwwU7E.jpg&h=55729224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOuhe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOuhe4.jpg&h=a6d636f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVCGSoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVCG